* ISO 20022\nBusiness Application Header (head)
** Role
*** Routing envelope for a message
*** Separates routing from payload
*** head.001 BAH, head.002 File Header
** Routing fields
*** Fr — From (sender)
*** To — receiver
*** BizMsgIdr — Business Message Identifier
*** MsgDefIdr — Message Definition Identifier
*** CreDt — Creation date-time
** Context fields
*** BizSvc — Business Service
*** MktPrctc — Market Practice
*** Prty — Priority
*** BizPrcgDt — Business Processing Date
** Integrity and linking
*** Sgntr — Signature
*** Rltd — Related (prior header)
*** CpyDplct / PssblDplct
** Business File Header
*** head.002 groups many messages
*** PyldDesc — Payload Description
@endmindmap
